OL,3,CProvisional IRA victims discontinue
OL,4,Ccivil claim against Gerry Adams
OL,6,FThree victims of Provisional IRA
OL,7,Fbombings in England will discontinue
OL,8,Ftheir damages claim against former
OL,9,FSinn Fein president Gerry Adams, their
OL,10,Flawyers have told the High Court.
OL,12,FMr Adams was being sued for #1 in
OL,13,Fdamages by three men injured in the
OL,14,Fblasts in the 1970s and 1990s.
OL,26,@qD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
