OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774120269
OL,3,CProvisional IRA victims discontinue
OL,4,Ccivil claim against Gerry Adams
OL,6,FJohn Clark, a victim of the 1973 Old
OL,7,FBailey bombing in London; Jonathan
OL,8,FGanesh, a 1996 London Docklands
OL,9,Fbombing victim; and Barry Laycock, a
OL,10,Fvictim of the 1996 Arndale shopping
OL,11,Fcentre bombing in Manchester, all
OL,12,Falleged that Mr Adams was a leading
OL,13,Fmember of the Provisional IRA on those
OL,14,Fdates, including of its Army Council.
OL,16,FThe former Sinn Fein president denied
OL,17,Fthe allegations and was defending the
OL,18,Fclaim, telling the court earlier this
OL,19,Fweek that he had "no involvement
OL,20,Fwhatsoever" in the bombings and was
OL,21,Fnever a member of the Provisional IRA.
OL,26,@xD@Rrr{D@ROU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774120269
OL,3,CProvisional IRA victims discontinue
OL,4,Ccivil claim against Gerry Adams
OL,6,FOn Friday, the last day of the two-
OL,7,Fweek trial, Anne Studd KC, for the
OL,8,Fvictims, told the High Court that the
OL,9,Fclaim would be discontinued with "no
OL,10,Forder as to costs" after "proceedings
OL,11,Fdeveloped overnight".
OL,13,FMr Adams was not in court on Friday.
OL,15,FIn written submissions for the trial,
OL,16,FMs Studd said that the three men
OL,17,Fclaimed that none of the bombings
OL,18,F"took place without the knowledge and
OL,19,Fagreement" of Mr Adams in his role in
OL,20,Fthe Provisional IRA and of its seven-
OL,21,Fman Army Council.
OL,26,@qD@bOUrD@RO]rD@ZOUsD@TO]zD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774120269
OL,3,CProvisional IRA victims discontinue
OL,4,Ccivil claim against Gerry Adams
OL,6,FShe continued that the men believed
OL,7,Fthat Mr Adams was "as involved as the
OL,8,Fpeople who planted and detonated those
OL,9,Fbombs".
OL,11,FIn his evidence, Mr Adams said that
OL,12,Fopponents of Sinn Fein, of which he
OL,13,Fwas president from 1983 to 2018, "have
OL,14,Frepeatedly sought to conflate" the
OL,15,Fparty with the Provisional IRA, and
OL,16,Fstressed that they are "separate
OL,17,Forganisations".
OL,26,@oD@SOUqD@FO]tD@TrruD@bOUvD@^O]xD@XOUyD@
OL,26,ANO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774120269
OL,3,CProvisional IRA victims discontinue
OL,4,Ccivil claim against Gerry Adams
OL,6,FHe continued that he had "no
OL,7,Finvolvement in or advance knowledge
OL,8,Fof" any of the bombings, and was
OL,9,F"never a member of the IRA or its Army
OL,10,FCouncil", telling the court on Tuesday
OL,11,Fthat he was "glad that the IRA has
OL,12,Fleft the stage".
OL,14,FHe also said that while he believed in
OL,15,Fthe "broad principle that people have
OL,16,Fthe right to resist occupation", he
OL,17,Fwas "very, very clear that there were
OL,18,Fdastardly things that were done that
OL,19,Fshould never have been done".
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@CO]qD@AOUrD@HO]sD@MOUtD@OO]wD@
OL,26,AEOUxD@_O]yD@EOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774120269
OL,3,CProvisional IRA victims discontinue
OL,4,Ccivil claim against Gerry Adams
OL,6,FEdward Craven KC, for Mr Adams, told
OL,7,Fthe court in London that evidence that
OL,8,FMr Adams was involved in the bombings
OL,9,Fwas "extremely limited and we say
OL,10,Fbordering on non-existent".
OL,12,FThe barrister also said that the claim
OL,13,Fshould be dismissed for being brought
OL,14,Ftoo late, suggesting that the three
OL,15,Fmen were using the claim to try to
OL,16,Fhave a "public inquiry-style" hearing
OL,17,Finto finding historical truths.
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@ZO]xD@HOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1774120269
OL,3,CProvisional IRA victims discontinue
OL,4,Ccivil claim against Gerry Adams
OL,6,FHe added: "The desire to establish for
OL,7,Fthe historical record that Mr Adams
OL,8,Fwas a member of the IRA is the purpose
OL,9,Fthat has driven this claim," adding
OL,10,Fthat this could be an abuse of the
OL,11,Fcourt system.
OL,13,FIn their evidence, the three men said
OL,14,Fthe reasons they did not bring claims
OL,15,Fearlier were that they did not realise
OL,16,Fthey could do so, could not afford it,
OL,17,Fwere suffering from mental or physical
OL,18,Finjuries and feared violent reprisals.
